{
  "texts": [
    "(14), which assumes a constant n T at all scales.",
    "The fractional energy density spectrum obtained from the maximum a posteriori parameter values is plotted in Fig. 16.",
    "We have so far considered a primordial background to be the only source of GWs in our data.",
    "We now recall that the most plausible and loud source of a GW background at these frequencies remains that of a SMBHB background.",
    "It is therefore likely that any signature for a cosmological background needs to be considered in parallel with a SMBHB background, or in this case more accurately termed 'foreground'."
  ]
}